## Step 4
Simplifying the first inequality, we get $1-x \geq 2x \Rightarrow 1 \geq 3x \Rightarrow x \leq \frac{1}{3}$. This condition applies when $x$ is the shorter segment and $1-x$ is the longer segment, implying $x < 0.5$.

